_sText:
One of my first creations :-)
It's a small based AWP-Map with 2 Towers on each side.
The Map is bug-free so far I think, I couldnt enjoy the Gameplay with more than 16 Players so I just think more than 16 players are possible.

I hope people will try-out that Map, it's some relict from my first Mapping-days. :-O
